Package com.hms_networks.americas.sc.azure.data

Classes to manage and build payloads for sending to Azure in the Ewon Flexy Generic Azure Connector.

See: Description

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AZConnectorPayload
    Abstract payload class that stores data points and provides a method for tracking when the payload is ready to send.
    AZConnectorPayloadAllRecent
    Azure payload class that only includes at most one value for a tag in the output payload String.
    AZConnectorPayloadArray
    Azure payload class that adds each payload to a JSON array called datapoints and has no added constraints.
    AZConnectorPayloadManager
    Class for managing data points that are ready to be sent as telemetry data to Azure as MQTT payloads.
    AZConnectorPayloadMostRecent
    Azure payload class that only includes at most one value for a tag in the output payload String.
